---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="AEM Recommendation Generator" description="AEM Recommendation generator is a content based recommendation engine which reads the metadata from pages and finds the similar pages to generate the recommendations." canonicalUrl={`https://www.codebrains.co.in${Astro.url.pathname}`}>
    <div class="intro-header recommendations-home">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="recommendations-home-intro-message">
                    <h1><mark>AEM Recommendation Generator</mark></h1>
                    <h3><mark>Content Based Recommendation Engine in AEM</mark></h3>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="container main-container">
    <h1>AEM Recommendation Generator</h1>

    <br>
    <p class="lead">The AEM Recommendation generator is a content based recommendation engine which reads the metadata
        from pages and finds the similar pages to generate the recommendations, this tool leverages Apache Commons Math 3
        library which is a lightweight library for performing statistical & mathematical calculations
        for generating the content based recommendations.</p>

    <br>
    <p class="lead">A recommendation engine can enhance the user experience by providing recommendations based on the
        data already available within the AEM system, these recommendation can range from a similar page recommendation on
        a blog to a product recommendation in case of an ecommerce website.</p>

    <h4>&nbsp;</h4>
    <div class="video-container">
        <iframe class="video" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/oIvR_zifp6o" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>
    <h4>&nbsp;</h4>
    <ul class="footer-social">
        <li>
            Github link : <a href="https://github.com/ankit-gubrani/aem-recommendation-engine" class="fa fa-github" target="_blank"></a>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <h3>Configuring AEM Recommendation Generator :</h3>
    <p class="lead">Follow this <a href="https://www.codebrains.co.in/recommendation-engine/configure" target="_blank">link</a> for configuring the AEM Recommendation Generator.</p>
    <h3>AEM Recommendation Generator Approach :</h3>
    <p class="lead">Follow this <a href="https://www.codebrains.co.in/recommendation-engine/approach" target="_blank">link</a> to go over the overall approach used for implementing AEM Recommendation Generator.</p>

    <br>
</div>
</BaseLayout>
